--- required packages
git
cmake
python2.7
python-pip

--- binaries / libraries are compiled for x64

--- how to build
./gen-proto.sh
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
make

--- black box tests 
- build first
- then
cd test
submit-transfer.sh

- this will start Gradido_Node and test data will be in 
  /tmp/ncd-output.yaml (by default); check /steps
